{"tid":1698542,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬里國家隊將會有三個Adama Traore","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T19:04:25.000Z","uid":34572,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4aea60b19075cb5a5d052de63f6e7df50dceffa0","tid":1698542,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"Last June, Monaco&rsquo;s Adama Traore scored for Mali. <br />\n<br />\nHe was then replaced by Metz&rsquo;s Adama Traore who also scored. <br />\n<br />\nNow Wolves&rsquo; Adama Traore has declared for Mali, meaning Adama Traore, Adama Traore and Adama Traore all represent the same international team 🤯<br />\n<br />\n宜家狼隊A查都決定咗代表馬里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ff9c2e52862104ba00ab02bb8ced5f55215bfe","tid":1698542,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"回帶6月<br />\n<strong>【非國盃】同名同姓球員齊入波 馬里有幾多個阿達馬查奧爾？</strong><br />\n馬里這兩位阿達馬查奧爾（Adama Traor&eacute;）同樣在1995年6月出世，6月5日出生的那位名氣稍遜，司職翼鋒，現效梅斯，上曾被外借至奧連斯，在今場馬里對毛里塔尼亞中，他先擔任後備。為了方便分辨兩人，先叫翼鋒阿達馬查奧爾做「大查奧爾」。<br />\n<br />\n6月28日出世的那位阿達馬查奧爾就名氣大得多，他在2015年的世青盃十分搶鏡，攻入4球並交出3次助攻，助馬里贏得季軍，他個人還得到世青盃金球獎。這名中場阿達馬查奧爾踢過里爾，現效摩納哥，但上季被外借至布魯日舒高，就叫他做「細查奧爾」。<br />\n<br />\n在埃及時間昨日（6月24日）的非國盃E組首輪，馬里鬥毛里塔尼亞，細查奧爾正選上陣踢攻中，在37分鐘先助攻艾度拿爾戴亞比（Abdoulay Diaby）開紀錄。其後，馬里前鋒馬利加（Moussa Marega）射入12碼，為馬里半場領先2：0。<br />\n<br />\n換邊後，是兩位阿達馬查奧爾移形換影的舞台。細查奧爾在55分鐘中路突破，擺脫對方守衛，在禁區頂拉弓一射破網，助馬里贏到3：0。61分鐘，身披21號球衣的細查奧爾被換離場，由14號球衣的大查奧爾入替。<br />\n<br />\n雖然毛里塔尼亞在72分鐘破蛋，但大查奧爾在73分鐘射入世界波，他在右路推入大位，禁區頂起腳一熨，皮球直飛網窩，最終馬里靠兩位阿達馬查奧爾各入一球，以4：1大勝毛里塔尼亞。"},{"pid":"639191505f0a29b6d45a2cd3223f8e94dd7330ba","tid":1698542,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef0539fecfaf6e346f07347a88f0ad84a60e0a1","tid":1698542,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"34aff9967ab6f554de0e7adaa5786e98a9d50188","tid":1698542,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9Jfumx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9Jfumx.png&h=cbe64e25&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n值得一提嘅係，今季法甲嗰兩個Traore今季都喺梅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8baed8dbd05f356bb9a0d102612d065a8e0d5c1a","tid":1698542,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"可惜其中一件A查係中場，唔係嘅話可以排A查三箭頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fd9310ba2bf4175d49b399c09894afdfed1fca","tid":1698542,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"公廁名"},{"pid":"3ab4e0231b4602eba528613ab298dbcebcf4bf6b","tid":1698542,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34aff9967ab6f554de0e7adaa5786e98a9d50188","tid":1698542,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9Jfumx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9Jfumx.png&h=cbe64e25&s={SIZE}\" 